    <p>
      This is a wonderful way to see the Albert Dock from the water. Lisa will
      be leading a flotilla of paddleboarders and Paul will be heading up the
      flock of kayaks.
    </p>

    <!-- TODO
    <p>
      Please tell xxx on xxx if you’d like to join us and we’ll book you a place.
