      <%= partial(:map_link, :locals => { :name => 'Meet at Liverpool watersports centre', :url => 'https://goo.gl/maps/qgXoYsGZQSM2' }) %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <i class="fas fa-location-arrow fa-fw"></i>
      Getting there: 20 minute walk from the city centre or short taxi journey.
